            <h1>Help & Support</h1>
            <p>If you've experienced discrimination in Germany, you're not alone. Here are some resources that can provide support and assistance:</p>

            <h2>National Anti-Discrimination Bodies</h2>

            <h3>Federal Anti-Discrimination Agency (Antidiskriminierungsstelle des Bundes)</h3>
            <p>This is the main government body responsible for enforcing anti-discrimination laws in Germany.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Website: <a href="https://www.antidiskriminierungsstelle.de/EN/home/home_node.html" target="_blank">www.antidiskriminierungsstelle.de</a></li>
                <li>Phone: +49 (0) 30 18555-1855</li>
                <li>Email: beratung@ads.bund.de</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>German Institute for Human Rights (Deutsches Institut f√ºr Menschenrechte)</h3>
            <p>An independent institution that promotes and protects human rights in Germany.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Website: <a href="https://www.institut-fuer-menschenrechte.de/en/homepage" target="_blank">www.institut-fuer-menschenrechte.de</a></li>
                <li>Phone: +49 (0)30 259 359-0</li>
                <li>Email: info@institut-fuer-menschenrechte.de</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Non-Governmental Organizations</h2>

            <h3>PRO ASYL</h3>
            <p>An independent organization advocating for refugee rights and against racism.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Website: <a href="https://www.proasyl.de/en/" target="_blank">www.proasyl.de</a></li>
                <li>Phone: +49 (0)69 242 314 20</li>
                <li>Email: proasyl@proasyl.de</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Amadeu Antonio Foundation</h3>
            <p>A foundation working to strengthen democratic civic society and eliminate neo-Nazism, right-wing extremism, and antisemitism.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Website: <a href="https://www.amadeu-antonio-stiftung.de/en/" target="_blank">www.amadeu-antonio-stiftung.de</a></li>
                <li>Phone: +49 (0)30 240 886 10</li>
                <li>Email: info@amadeu-antonio-stiftung.de</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Legal Aid</h2>

            <h3>German Bar Association (Deutscher Anwaltverein)</h3>
            <p>Can help you find a lawyer specializing in anti-discrimination cases.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Website: <a href="https://anwaltauskunft.de/en" target="_blank">anwaltauskunft.de</a></li>
                <li>Phone: +49 (0)30 726 152 0</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Counseling Services</h2>

            <h3>Counseling Network for Victims of Right-wing, Racist and Antisemitic Violence (VBRG)</h3>
            <p>Provides support and counseling for victims of hate crimes and discrimination.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Website: <a href="https://www.verband-brg.de/english/" target="_blank">www.verband-brg.de</a></li>
                <li>Email: info@verband-brg.de</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Emergency Contacts</h2>
            <p>In case of immediate danger or emergency situations:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Police: 110</li>
                <li>Emergency Services: 112</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Remember, you have rights in Germany, regardless of your immigration status. Don't hesitate to seek help if you've experienced discrimination or unfair treatment.</p>
